          "description": "",
          "inputSection": {
            "components": [
              {
                "type": "input",
                "subType": "alert",
                "header": "",
                "content": "To get you started with AWS DeepRacer, you will receive 10 free hours to train or evaluate models and 5GB of free storage during your first month. This is enough to train your first time-trial model, evaluate it, tune it, and then enter it into the AWS DeepRacer League. This offer is valid for 30 days after you have used the service for the first time.",
